      <title>加纳反 LGBTQ 法之争威胁到 200 亿美元债务交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ghana-s-feud-over-anti-lgbtq-law-threatens-20-billion-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果阿克拉选择继续实施践踏银行反歧视标准的惩罚性法律，世界银行将面临融资困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ghana-s-feud-over-anti-lgbtq-law-threatens-20-billion-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:01:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>犯罪及其对经济造成的 400 亿美元损失是南非投票的核心</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日益加剧的不安全感和腐败是 5 月 29 日选举前夕的主要问题，预计选举将迫使非洲人国民大会做出权力分享安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/crime-corruption-are-key-issues-at-heart-of-south-african-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 04:00:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯恢复对乌克兰发电厂和网络的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ukraine-s-kyiv-lviv-under-attack-after-more-than-1-month-pause</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯在暂停两周后恢复对乌克兰电力生产和配电网络的攻击，目标是全国各地的设施，包括首都和西部靠近波兰边境的利沃夫。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-08/ukraine-s-kyiv-lviv-under-attack-after-more-than-1-month-pause</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 May 2024 03:57:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平称赞东欧在欧盟关系陷入动荡之际“有帮助”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-xi-arrives-in-serbia-to-bolster-ties-with-europe-s-east</link>
      <description><![CDATA[习近平主席抵达贝尔格莱德，旨在提升中国作为贸易伙伴的潜力，他称赞中国与东欧的关系为世界第二大经济体带来了福音。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/china-s-xi-arrives-in-serbia-to-bolster-ties-with-europe-s-east</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 20:05:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>谈判陷入僵局，以色列逼近拉法，局势高度紧张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列控制进入埃及的拉法口岸的举动引发了对其最终目标的激烈争论：这是长期威胁入侵加沙南部城市的开始，还是试图向哈马斯施压，要求放宽停火条件以及释放人质？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/israel-edges-into-rafah-with-tensions-high-over-deadlocked-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 14:31:05 GMT</pubDate>
